📦 PortSync Lanka
Smart Port & Logistics Management System
📖 Overview

PortSync Lanka is a modern web-based Port & Logistics Management System designed to streamline shipment tracking, container monitoring, document classification, and report generation within a port environment.

The system is inspired by operational structures used in organizations such as the Sri Lanka Ports Authority and aims to improve efficiency, transparency, and digital transformation in port logistics management.

🎯 Project Objectives

Enable real-time shipment tracking

Manage container status updates with history logs

Digitally classify official port documents

Generate automated PDF reports

Implement secure role-based access control

🚀 Features
📦 Shipment Tracking

Add and manage shipment details

Track vessel name, origin, ETA, status

Search and filter shipments

🚢 Container Management

Link containers to shipments

Update container status (At Sea, At Port, Cleared, Released)

Track yard location

Maintain update history logs

📄 Document Classification

Upload and manage port-related documents

Categorize documents (Request, Approval, Report, Financial, Legal, etc.)

Search and filter by category

📊 Dashboard & Analytics

View total active shipments

Monitor container statistics

Visual data charts

Real-time overview panel

📑 PDF Report Generation

Daily shipment reports

Monthly container reports

Document summary reports

Downloadable PDF format

🏗 System Architecture
Frontend

React.js

Tailwind CSS / Material UI

Responsive Design

Backend

Node.js

Express.js

Database

MongoDB / MySQL

Authentication

JWT (JSON Web Token)

🧑‍💼 User Roles

Super Admin

Admin

Port Officer

Clerk

Viewer

Each role has controlled access based on permissions.

