⚙ Installation & Setup
1️⃣ Clone the Repository
git clone https://github.com/your-username/portsync-lanka.git
cd portsync-lanka
2️⃣ Install Dependencies
npm install
3️⃣ Run the Frontend
npm start
4️⃣ Run Backend (if separated)
npm run dev
